You have two tables:

Employee
emp_id	emp_name	dept_id
Department
dept_id	dept_name

Write SQL query to:

fetch all employees
along with department names
even if department is missing

Expected concept: LEFT JOIN
------------------------------------------------------
1. select e.emp_id, e.emp_name, d.dept_name
    from employee e
    left join department d
    on e.dept_id = d.dept_id